Package: tockycode
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.8), python3-pip, python3-venv
Maintainer: TockyCode Team <info@tockycode.com>
Description: Professional AI Code Generator - 100% Free, Local
 TockyCode is a professional AI-powered code generation tool that runs
 entirely on your local machine. No internet connection required.
 .
 Features:
  * Generate professional code in multiple languages
  * Local AI models (offline capable)
  * CLI and GUI interfaces
  * Analyze code quality
  * Interactive code generation mode
 .
 Supported languages: Python, JavaScript, Java, C++, Go, Rust, TypeScript, and more.
